Potato skins were thick slices of uncooked potato. Clam chowder was off and gross tasting. The gravy on the poutine was cold. Great beer selection, if they bring you the right one. Burgers have been decent in the past but I didn't have one on my last visit.
The food and atmosphere was great
Great food. Great service. Welcoming vibe.  Highly recommended.
